Class CustomUpgradeItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.yeetmanlord.bedwars_zeta.api.bedwars_menus.items.upgrade.UpgradeItem
      • com.github.yeetmanlord.bedwars_zeta.api.bedwars_menus.items.upgrade.CustomUpgradeItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICustomMenuItem, IMenuItem, com.github.yeetmanlord.zeta_core.sql.ISQL<UpgradeItem>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExampleCustomUpgradeItem

    public abstract class CustomUpgradeItem
extends UpgradeItem
implements ICustomMenuItem
    A custom shop item that can be bought in the upgrade's menu. This is a base class for all custom upgrade items. To create a custom upgrade item, extend this class and implement the methods.

    You must also override the getSQLData() method to return a Row object that contains the data for the item. This data will be used to save the item to the database.
